    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3124080/extras/c51848466cb813ac7cbab5a734c8ebad.poster.avif?t=1767810977\" width=620 height=123 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3124080/extras/c51848466cb813ac7cbab5a734c8ebad.webm?t=1767810977\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><br>Welcome to the world of Cardaire!<br><br>In Cardaire you take the role of &quot;Mulligan&quot;, an intrepid duelist who aims to make a name for herself in a world that revolves around a card game (how neat). Embark on a strange adventure through the <strong>Duelist Frontier</strong> to prove yourself as a real Duelist. Collect cards, purchase booster packs, duel foes, and build your perfect deck!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3124080/extras/eefeee396f1450595b65ea31e1c7ef2b.poster.avif?t=1767810977\" width=620 height=348 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3124080/extras/eefeee396f1450595b65ea31e1c7ef2b.webm?t=1767810977\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3124080/extras/eefeee396f1450595b65ea31e1c7ef2b.mp4?t=1767810977\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3124080/extras/c2cecf6ffd24c35933c7417d7c77688a.avif?t=1767810977\" width=620 height=123 /></span><br><br>This game includes:<br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Over 100 unique cards<br></li><li> A world packed with things to explore and characters to meet<br></li><li> A homemade soundtrack including REAL - ACTUAL - MUSIC<br></li><li> Some relaxing fishing content<br></li><li> Unique and challenging duels - including repeatable mini-tournaments<br></li><li> At least (one) clown</li></ul><br>This game <strong>does not</strong> include:<br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> AI Art<br></li><li> NFTs<br></li><li> Microtransactions<br></li><li> A second clown (probably)</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3124080/extras/7ba4c3d19f943318c145f8a0a79c9e8a.poster.avif?t=1767810977\" width=620 height=348 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3124080/extras/7ba4c3d19f943318c145f8a0a79c9e8a.webm?t=1767810977\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3124080/extras/7ba4c3d19f943318c145f8a0a79c9e8a.mp4?t=1767810977\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3124080/extras/bec847469c79e6db7cb1a15700a83621.avif?t=1767810977\" width=620 height=123 /></span><br><br>Hey there I'm &quot;aeiou&quot;, and I'm the developer behind this thing! For as long as I can remember I've been cursed with the ungodly affliction of &quot;enjoying card games&quot;. Growing up, when I wasn't scraping together money to buy more packs I was playing videogames that offered the 'card game experience'. I fell in love with the adventure of starting from nothing, piecing together your first deck, fighting to get more cards, and then finally becoming a powerhouse duelist. I'm making Cardaire to capture that experience for my fellow cardboard enthusiasts.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3124080/extras/da94f865ad3f44697619f7e6f216cd94.apng?t=1767810977\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3124080/extras/da94f865ad3f44697619f7e6f216cd94.poster.avif?t=1767810977\" class=\"bb_img\" width=620 height=123 /></picture></span>",
